          value of statistical life of <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$4.8 million</NUMEX> in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1990</TIMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">US</ENAMEX>
          dollars, which can be translated into an approximate
